OL,3,CIn-patient hospice unit to remain
OL,4,Cpermanently closed
OL,6,FEnd of life charity Marie Curie says
OL,7,Fit has taken the "difficult decision"
OL,8,Fto not reopen the inpatient unit at
OL,9,Fone of its hospices.
OL,11,FThe 26-bed unit in Woolton, in
OL,12,FLiverpool, closed in July 2024 due to
OL,13,Fa shortage in specialised nursing
OL,14,Fstaff.
OL,16,FThe closure sparked a number of
OL,17,Fprotests by campaigners and bereaved
OL,18,Ffamilies who made passionate pleas for
OL,19,Fthe unit to reopen, raising concerns
OL,20,Fabout the provision of palliative care
OL,21,Fin Liverpool.
