OL,3,CIn-patient hospice unit to remain
OL,4,Cpermanently closed
OL,6,FThe charity said its Board of Trustees
OL,7,Ftook the decision to permanently close
OL,8,Fthe unit after the Cheshire and
OL,9,FMerseyside Integrated Care Board could
OL,10,Fnot commit to more funding.
OL,12,FThe hospice said it will remain open
OL,13,Ffor services including outpatient
OL,14,Fclinics, and the building on Speke
OL,15,FRoad will be a base for Marie Curie's
OL,16,FNorth West team.
