OL,3,CIn-patient hospice unit to remain
OL,4,Cpermanently closed
OL,6,FIn a statement, Marie Curie Chief
OL,7,FExecutive Matthew Reed said the
OL,8,Fcharity is "fully committed to the
OL,9,Fpeople of Liverpool" and that end of
OL,10,Flife or palliative care will continue
OL,11,Fto be provided through its 'Enhanced
OL,12,FHospice Care at Home service'.
OL,14,FMr Reed said: "We understand it will
OL,15,Fbe difficult news for future patients,
OL,16,Four staff and volunteers and the local
OL,17,Fcommunity and we thank them for their
OL,18,Fsupport through a period of
OL,19,Funcertainty.
