OL,3,CIn-patient hospice unit to remain
OL,4,Cpermanently closed
OL,6,F"I would like to assure all those who
OL,7,Fneed end of life or palliative care
OL,8,Fnow that we continue to provide this
OL,9,Fthrough our Enhanced Hospice Care at
OL,10,FHome service - which we seek to expand
OL,11,Ffurther - and our outpatient clinics
OL,12,Fthrough which we can support more
OL,13,Fpeople with the funds we have
OL,14,Favailable.
OL,16,F"We will also continue to work closely
OL,17,Fwith other hospices and hospitals in
OL,18,FLiverpool when patients need inpatient
OL,19,Fcare.
