OL,3,CIn-patient hospice unit to remain
OL,4,Cpermanently closed
OL,6,F"Like our partners at the ICB, we
OL,7,Fbelieve everyone should have access to
OL,8,Fhigh quality palliative and end of
OL,9,Flife care and we remain totally
OL,10,Fcommitted to play a part in delivering
OL,11,Fthis for the people of Liverpool,
OL,12,Frecognising that most end of life care
OL,13,Fis already provided outside hospice
OL,14,Fbuildings.
OL,16,F"Both the ICB and Marie Curie face
OL,17,Fsignificant financial deficits; as a
OL,18,Fcharity, we must ensure our finances
OL,19,Fare sustainable and our finite funds
OL,20,Fbenefit as many people as possible.
