OL,4,Cpermanently closed
OL,6,F"We remain fully committed to working
OL,7,Fwith the ICB and our partners to find
OL,8,Fsustainable ways to provide for
OL,9,Fpalliative and end of life care -
OL,10,Fincluding inpatient beds - in
OL,11,FLiverpool.
OL,13,F"We need to reach a long-term solution
OL,14,Fwith government and healthcare system
OL,15,Fpartners as costs rise, and demand
OL,16,Fgrows.
